  "description_short": "Adulting Credit LLC is a credit repair provider based in Seattle, Washington. Rated 5.0/5 on Google.",
  "description_long": "Adulting Credit LLC is a credit repair provider serving clients in Seattle, Washington. The company serves consumers in the Seattle area who are looking to repair and improve their credit scores.\n\nAdulting Credit LLC specializes in credit repair services designed to help consumers repair and improve their credit scores.\n\nWhen evaluating credit repair services in Seattle, consumers should look for providers that dispute directly with all three credit bureaus \u2014 Equifax, Experian, and TransUnion. Key differentiators include transparency around pricing, realistic timelines for results, and whether the company offers a money-back guarantee. Adulting Credit LLC operates in a highly regulated industry under the Credit Repair Organizations Act (CROA), which requires written contracts, a three-day cancellation window, and prohibits upfront fees before services are rendered.\n\nConsumers in the Seattle, Washington area who are considering Adulting Credit LLC should contact the company directly to discuss their specific situation and get current pricing information. As with any credit repair provider, it is advisable to compare multiple options, verify licensing and credentials, and read recent customer reviews before making a decision.",
